short_description: Start The Cooking Game, learn to cook, serve and manage your own restaurants. Show your skills and feed the hungry customers!

name: Battlerite
short_description: BATTLERITE‚Äã ‚Äãis‚Äã ‚Äãan‚Äã ‚Äãaction-packed‚Äã ‚Äãteam‚Äã ‚Äãarena‚Äã ‚Äãbrawler.‚Äã ‚ÄãExperience‚Äã ‚Äãthe‚Äã ‚Äãunique‚Äã ‚Äãcombination‚Äã ‚Äãof‚Äã top-down‚Äã ‚Äãshooter‚Äã meets‚Äã ‚Äãfast-paced‚Äã ‚Äãfighting‚Äã ‚Äãgame and challenge ‚Äãfriends‚Äã ‚Äãand‚Äã foes‚Äã ‚Äãin‚Äã ‚Äãa‚Äã ‚Äãbattle‚Äã ‚Äãof reaction. The Arena awaits!

name: Detective Hayseed - Hollywood
short_description: The list of Oscar winners has been stolen as part of a nefarious plot to overturn the established Hollywood order. Our hero has to struggle through a series of tests and tasks in order to uncover the clues as to who has done it. And, of course, to stop him carrying out his threat.

name: Along the Edge
short_description: Along the Edge is a visual novel set in the European countryside, where your choices impact the main character's personality and appearance.

name: Optika
short_description: Discover the world of light physics: play with lasers, prisms, mirrors, magnets and dozens of other optical devices. Explore the world of Optika with Prof. Opticus and his assistant, Sofia! Research and complete more than one hundred challenging puzzles!

name: Escape from Pleasure Planet
short_description: Escape from Pleasure Planet is a gay-themed science-fiction adventure game with bright colourful graphics, a fun story and character art by Joe Phillips.

name: Malazard: Magic Defense
short_description: Unleash the magic inside you!Purify the demonic legion with a set of powerful abilities.The collapsing world relies upon you, experience what it means to control all Magic!

name: StarSmashers
short_description: You are Captain Carter, of the Space Beagle. Ahead lies an army lead by the scumbag Kaldor Seth, he will obliterate all who oppose him in his pursuit of power. Carefully manage your ships weapons and defenses to bring your enemies to their knees!

name: Team Racing League
short_description: In this unique 3 on 3 racegame, it's up to you and your teammates to finish before the opposing team does. Mastering the high quality vehicle handling, special abilities, and optimal Team Strategy are key to win the race.

name: Salvaged
short_description: The human race explores the stars, but a keen focus on the future has left a trail of desolation in the past. You are Alex Pieterson, commander of the salvage ship Thaddeus and its team of hardened agents. You are a remnant of that past, fighting for survival in a huge new galaxy.

name: The God's Chain
short_description: Finally the day came when we found our GOD.Human Beings are an experiment done by them.The human beings are evolving and have become one of the greatest powers in the universe which is becoming a great problem for other colonies in the universe.So our god decides to end the experiment but now human beings will fight for their existence.

name: Hover Havoc
short_description: Grab 3 friends, 4 controllers and pick your craft... then battle, bump and bounce opponents into ‚Äòhoverific‚Äô submission! A fun fueled pickup 'n play party game; drift through a multitude of arenas in a blur of hover-fueled rampage!

name: The Unwelcomed
short_description: The Unwelcomed is an escape the room (EtR) type game created for VR and was inspired by such classics as Crimson Room. The Unwelcomed starts by inviting you to come to your late uncle's mansion to claim it as your own. Once you arrive, however, it's going to be hard to leave...

name: Fictorum
short_description: Fictorum is an action RPG featuring destructible environments, a procedural node-based world map, and dynamic magic shaping.

name: INVASION!
short_description: Narrated by Ethan Hawke and created by the director of Madagascar, INVASION! is a colorful VR animated short about a duo of aliens with grand ambitions to take over our world. Instead, they are greeted by two adorable, white bunnies‚Ä¶..and you are one of them! Come experience what happens!

name: Fenimore Fillmore: The Westerner
short_description: Fenimore Fillmore: The Westerner. Originally released in 2004 was the best adventures of the year in different countries, and won many awards. Fenimore Fillmore is back now on Steam on amazing remastered version.

name: The Seeker
short_description: Welcome to the Seeker! Run, hide and hack in this indie top-down game that gives a whole new meaning to the word "random!" Explore a virtually infinite number of levels as you avoid dangerous turrets, enemies and alarms. Find the exit to destroy the AI and avenge all of humanity!

name: Starship Disco
short_description: Starship Disco‚Ñ¢ is a music-driven rhythm shooter with user music imports. Blast aliens to the beat in VR with 1 or 2 hands with HTC Vive or Oculus Touch controllers.

name: Fall of Freya (Alpha 1)
short_description: Sci-Fi Survival Shooter created by a small indie team. Powered by the Unreal Engine 4.

name: Void
short_description: Feel the inhuman tension of outer space - floating between bits of debris - struggling to conserve air and fuel - experiencing a hauntingly personal tragedy.

name: Saving Harmony
short_description: It is March 15, 1920 and the town of Nikolayevsk-on-Amur has been overrun by mad men killing and burning everything in sight. You are the last survivor of the Japanese expeditionary force in Siberia. You must fight to survive and in the end find a way to save Harmony.

name: SPLASH BLAST PANIC
short_description: SPLASH BLAST PANIC is a multiplayer competitive party game where you must shoot, ram, dodge and overall bully your opponents outside the screen with a variety of watergun-based weaponry.

name: Elven Assassin
short_description: Take a bow and kill hordes of orcs in the epic town defense game. You can play alone to conquer the leaderboards or unite with other assassins in online co-op mode. PS. Be careful to avoid massive axes thrown at you by orc warriors.

name: Ice Caves of Europa
short_description: Ice Caves of Europa will challenge your reflexes and your mind, blending free-flowing precision flight with confronting science fiction ideas about the nature of humanity. An inquisitive flying robot exploring the hazardous caves beneath Europa stumbles upon a sinister interplanetary conspiracy.

name: A Detective's Novel
short_description: On a cold November night in a desolate estate deep in the mountains an innocent life has prematurely perished and its up to the player to find out who did it.

name: The Life Of Greather
short_description: You are just a simple farmer, your wife has not returned. Venture across this open medieval world and find her.

name: Patterna
short_description: Patterna is a logic puzzle game for people who think that HexCells is far too easy. It features a highly customizable random level generator, a level editor, more than 70 levels, and an enchanting minimalist soundtrack by Alex Cottrell.

name: Candy Smash VR
short_description: Satisfy your hacking and slashing needs in colorful and mushy candy world. Experience the most fun you can have with VR and HTC Vive controllers smashing stuff!

name: Railway Empire
short_description: In Railway Empire, you will create an elaborate and wide-ranging rail network, purchase over 40 different trains modelled in extraordinary detail, and buy or build railway stations, maintenance buildings, factories and tourist attractions to keep your travel network ahead of the competition.

name: Star Tactics Redux
short_description: Turn-based strategy game full of spacefleet battles. 30+ hours of gameplay, randomized battles, huge campaign with different ways of completion. Experience infinite tactical situations and outsmart the tricky AI using dozens of ships and special abilities.

name: Will of the Gods
short_description: Will of the Gods is an arcade, strategy 1v1 game where players play as Gods, each trying to guide as many followers as they can to their temple, while punishing those who choose to follow the other God.

name: Detective Hank and the Golden Sneeze
short_description: When the Golden Sneeze is stolen from the Museum of Ancient History, it‚Äôs up to you, Detective Hank, to catch the thief. That will not be easy, as the culprit changes every new game. Puzzle your way through this steampunk themed, interactive whodunnit visual novel and bring the thief to justice!

name: Endless Fables: The Minotaur's Curse
short_description: Face off against the Minotaur!

name: Chernobyl VR Project
short_description: Visit Chernobyl without leaving home! Chernobyl VR Project is a unique project by The Farm 51, as it combines video games with educational and movie narrative software. It is the very first virtual tour around the Chernobyl and Pripyat area, compatible with VR headsets.

name: Planet Nomads
short_description: There's a whole planet of diverse biomes waiting for you to explore. Gather enough materials to build a mobile base that will carry everything a Nomad needs on a journey through an unknown land.

name: 3..2..1..Grenades!
short_description: 3..2..1..Grenades! is a snowball fight with high explosives. Help save Grenades Co from the terrible monster it's unleashed in this LOCAL MULTIPLAYER ADVENTURE GAME. Save the day or battle it out by yourself with bots, or with up to 4 of your friends!

name: Fairy Maids
short_description: Become the cleaning fairy!

name: Black Hat Cooperative
short_description: Black Hat Cooperative is a two player coop stealth game. One player is in VR, sneaking past enemies and collecting treasure. The other player is on the computer and keyboard, with access to a full view of the map and hacking superpowers. Work together to survive and complete the levels! Local multi-player supported.

name: Red is Dead - The Complex Fun Random Level Fast Strategy Game
short_description: Red is Dead is an intense action game with a randomized obstacle course containing over 120 levels. While playing this game you get an insane rush while being heavily amused. There are many physics in the game that you can interact with. Overcome insanely hard levels and beat your personal high score.

name: Dungeon Punks
short_description: Dungeon Punks is an old-school arcade beat-em-up, packed with new features like tag-team fighting gameplay and an RPG adventure! Nothing beats the thrill of freeze-blasting foes with a genie, as your dwarf tags in to incinerate them with bombs and napalm.

name: Frantic Freighter
short_description: THIS GAME IS OPTIMIZED FOR VR*, BUT DOES NOT REQUIRE IT. Frantically attempt a delivery across space in a freighter. Unfortunately, your ship is constantly falling apart. Trade spare parts, find stashes & evade pirates along the way. Succeed to unlock challenges!

name: miniLAW: Ministry of Law
short_description: Roam the dystopian future city of New Babel, Mankind's Last Hope, in search of crimes in progress. Use lethal weapons, non-lethal force, and diplomacy to take down bad guys.

name: Sentry Knight Tactics
short_description: Sentry Knight Tactics is a charming, cute action-strategy RPG adventure. Set in a land under siege by a transdimensional evil, you command your team of powerful heroes through various realms as you slaughter enemy hordes, complete quests, upgrade your gear and save the world.

name: Marble Land
short_description: Marble Land is a physics-based VR puzzle game in which the objective is to guide a marble into a designated target area by using various contraptions scattered across the level.

name: Maraiyum: Rise of the Setting Sun
short_description: The coup has finally come! After the disastrous rule of the previous Emperor, the Imperial army have placed you, a distant relative with no training, on the throne. With rebellions, religious insurgency, widespread famine, and a rapidly dwindling treasury, time is not on your side.

name: Super Star
short_description: You are a star agent in show biz as well as a fan of video games and animation as well. You have recently set up your own management company and are looking for someone with the talent. Although you have been trying hard, no one talented has been spotted yet. On night, you decided to play H-Game to cheer yourself up.

name: Dig 4 Destruction
short_description: The first of its kind! A first for VR! An intense online multiplayer deathmatch game where you must dig through the earth and excavate weapons to battle your enemies! *Coming Soon to the Oculus Touch!

name: White Noise 2
short_description: Enjoy a 4vs1 asymmetric horror experience like no other. Be a part of the investigator team, or take control of the creature and devour them!

name: Hospitalize
short_description: Find the most effective way to construct and manage a hospital. Build your hospital smart and avoid excess time and resources consumed by examining your patients unnecessary. You can choose to micromanage your patients or hope that your doctors are able to identify the cause of their symptoms.

name: Roomscale Tower
short_description: Roomscale Tower is a photogrammetric experience built for the HTC Vive. Become a knight of the Middle Ages and leave in search of wealth through towers filled with traps. Fight skeleton's army in intense survival mode. Climb mountains, catch piglets, throw knifes or relax at the tavern.

name: Four Last Things
short_description: Four Last Things is a point-and-click adventure game made from Renaissance-era paintings and public domain recordings of classical music. It is about sin, and the Four Last Things ‚Äì Death, Judgement, Heaven and Hell ‚Äì and strives to be intelligent and ridiculous in equal measures.

name: Zombie Camp
short_description: Zombie Camp is a room-scale VR shooter! Experience 360 degree virtual reality shooting in a desperate attempt to protect your campsite from crazed ZOMBIES!!

name: Space Rangers: Quest
short_description: SPACE RANGERS: QUEST is a new text adventure in the world of Space Rangers with a touch of nostalgia. Save the Coalition from the new threat!

name: Security Hole
short_description: Can you push through?! Security Hole is a challenging spatial puzzle with a cyberpunk story. You become a hacker who passes 3D virus blocks through security holes to save humanity. The game mechanics look like a workout tool for spatial thinking.

name: Mahluk:Dark Demon
short_description: Mahluk is a hack and slash platformer game with pixel-art style graphics and retro style addicting gameplay.

name: DYE
short_description: DYE is a challenging precision platformer where you help Hue rescue Pigments and defeat the nefarious Necrolights in order to restore color to the world! Jump, wall jump and float your way through 4 unique worlds with hundreds of challenges ranging from beginner to advanced level.

name: 911 Operator
short_description: Game about the difficult work of people that manage emergency lines and services. Answer incoming calls and react properly - give first aid instructions, advise, dispatch correct number of firemen / police / ambulances, or sometimes - just ignore the call. Play on ANY CITY in the world!

name: Duck Season
short_description: The game of your dreams just dropped, DUCK SEASON, a hunter with ridiculous graphics. Luckily, it's summer vacation and Mom just surprised you with a one day rental of it! Unfortunately, as you binge play it becomes apparent that all is not right with Duck Season...

name: The Multidimensional Underwear Drawer
short_description: The Multidimensional Underwear Drawer is an otome visual novel, in which young Hana finds eternal love ‚Ä¶ or death!

name: Autumn Park Mini Golf
short_description: Autumn Park Mini Golf is a first person miniature golf game set in a scenic park. With smooth jazz, piano, and Halloween music to help set the mood, we think you'll enjoy your time relaxing and exploring the park while you play. Can you finish the game under par?

name: Laser Lasso BALL
short_description: Laser Lasso BALL is the deadliest sport in the universe. Beings from across the galaxy battle to become stars in this Local Multiplayer Alien Deathsport.

name: 50 years
short_description: 50 Years is a fast-paced alternative to the bigger, longer turn-based strategy games. You can win or lose a game in a single evening. Either way you'll want to play it again.

name: Quest for Glory 1-5
short_description: The world of Gloriana, with all its wonderful diversity, awaits you.

name: Voodoo Garden
short_description: Welcome to the Voodoo Garden! You're owner of a little hut in a bustling swamp. With the help of little spirits you can earn powers and gold by producing various voodoo supplies.

name: Avalon: The Journey Begins
short_description: Depart your home world of Avalon to embark on the longest journey ever attempted by mankind, to find the end of the universe. What is at the end of the universe and where is the end of the universe? This is where your journey begins.

name: SENRAN KAGURA ESTIVAL VERSUS
short_description: Thrust into a parallel dimension, our buxom shinobi prepare for a new kind of beach-side battle. Can the islands‚Äô hosts be trusted? Will the other schools play fair? Will there be time to enjoy the beach before the fighting starts? Will anyone manage to keep their clothes intact?

name: Tank Hero VR
short_description: Tank Hero VR is developed by Edougame and also the first oriented VR platform tank game!!! During the battle players are placed in the real tank cockpit and control the tank to flight with others and it's really a fantasic game experience! Come and enjoy the Tank journey!!!

name: Batman‚Ñ¢: Arkham VR
short_description: Experience Gotham City through the eyes of the World's Greatest Detective in an all new Arkham mystery.

name: The Janitor
short_description: Max Taylor, a janitor, who is send to an abandoned asylum once guarded by the army. When he enters he gets in contact with a went-wrong experiment of the government and has to worry about his live! On the way to exit he has to struggle with the horrific manlike creature!

name: The Return Home Remastered
short_description: A rabbit's house is being attacked by reptile menaces from another dimension. With advanced portal technology, they can achieve conquest of the entire planet! In retaliation, the rabbit has decided to gather carrots to exchange for weapons which may allow him to fend off this threat.

name: Gunnihilation
short_description: Ultraviolent bullet-hell platformer Gunnihilation is dual stick 16-bit mayhem that fuses several forms of 2D shoot 'em up, from run-and-gun classics like Contra and Metal Slug, to the arena-based slaughter of Smash TV.

name: Calm Down, Stalin
short_description: Calm Down, Stalin is a game where you directly control your hands to threaten your enemies with nuclear weapons by moving your finger closer to The Button while signing important state papers, answering phone, dealing with your subordinates and most of all - fighting the stress of your position by smoking your pipe and any other available

name: Kisaragi no Hougyoku
short_description: Fujiwara Toru is a transfer student. At first glance he seems to be a generic, awkward teenager, but there is more to him than meets the eye. Sangu academy has a tradition called Ren. each year student choose a different grade partner, and all non partnered people are alone.

name: Azulgar: Star Commanders
short_description: Azulgar: Star Commanders is a Sci-Fi open world sandbox game that puts you in a command of your own custom made space ship. Explore aftermath of the Azulgar event that reshaped the face of the solar system.

name: Heroes from the Past: Joan of Arc
short_description: Save the day in this epic story of honor and courage

name: The Agency of Anomalies: Mystic Hospital Collector's Edition
short_description: Explore haunted military hospitals!

name: Off the Record: The Italian Affair Collector's Edition
short_description: Catch a ‚ÄòFoxy‚Äô thief!

name: Echoes of the Past: Kingdom of Despair Collector's Edition
short_description: Escape the witch's kingdom!

name: Invisible Mind
short_description: Go on a trip around the worlds created by your own mind and learn yourself.

name: Death's Life
short_description: Now you‚Äôre the new apprentice for Death. And it's your job to help gather souls. Only thing is, you can't just go and kill people to get the souls, it has to look natural. Like an accident. And that means setting up bottles, knives, brooms, and other regular objects in such a way as to create deadly chain reactions.

name: Drayt Empire
short_description: Drayt Empire is a classic RPG. Ronarke and Drayt, best Friends on an adventure to seek out and find the lost forbidden City of Rahland. On their travels they will encounter many challenges which will test their friendship and strength.

name: Interstellar Logistics Inc
short_description: Interstellar Logistics Inc. is an action puzzle game. The player shoots an object from Point A to Point B using the gravity of planets, stars, and black holes while hitting certain points along the way. There's a lot more to the game, but that is the basic idea.

name: Orczz
short_description: Orczz is a fantasy tower defense game set in the fantasy Kingdom of Whiteleaf, famous for its delicious honey wine ‚Äì the mead. The player controls the Knight Order of the Mug, protectors of Whiteleaf and the mead, who are once again called to defend the land against an invading horde of orcs.

name: Super Markup Man
short_description: Super Markup Man is the ultimate fun way to practice web development and learn the basics of HTML and CSS. No coding skills needed!

name: Monsters' Den: Book of Dread
short_description: Enter the Monsters' Den, a place of endless adventure, battle and reward! Lead your party of four heroes through each level of the ever-changing dungeon, fighting in turn-based battles and hunting for that elusive rare loot. The web-game classic comes to Steam!

name: You Deserve
short_description: "You Deserve" is an horror indie game in which you will experience a bullying story about revenge, starring a teenager called Amy who is lost in a world that she doesn‚Äôt know and her only objective is to escape from it without getting murdered.

name: BERSERK and the Band of the Hawk
short_description: Behold the fierce blend of "Warriors" and "Berserk"!

name: Heartomics: Lost Count
short_description: Battle humanoid "Heartomics" in this sexy shooter, Heartomics: Lost Count. A bullet hell game that uses fan service to entice players. Join us in the challenge to evade visually stunning shot patterns with thousands of bullets. Can you uncover the hidden mysteries!?

name: Boulder Dash - 30th Anniversary
short_description: Boulder Dash¬Æ - 30th Anniversary‚Ñ¢ features classic retro-style gameplay with 220 exciting levels across 11 new, gorgeous and unique worlds, and 10 playable characters. The new level editor and Steam Workshop support offers potentially infinite replay with both user as well as community-created levels.

name: Unbound
short_description: Unbound Early Access is the beginning of a new way to create and play with friends. Enjoy this first experience designed for VR and stay tuned for more!

name: Warhammer 40,000: Sanctus Reach
short_description: Warhammer 40,000: Sanctus Reach is a 3D turn-based strategy game like you‚Äôve never seen before: fast, immediate, deep, impressive to look at and incredibly fun! Fight through a dark era of carnage and endless war and lead the Space Wolves in a struggle to defend the last bastion of mankind.

name: Redactem
short_description: Rewind time and manipulate gravity in order to solve parkour puzzles in this exciting new 2D platformer.

name: Airport Fire Department - The Simulation
short_description: Move out with your team and experience tense missions. As a member of the airport fire department, you and your team extinguish massive aircraft fires and beat a path through the flickering flames.

name: Firefighters - The Simulation
short_description: You and your team will experience the exciting work of the professional fire brigade, surviving realistic missions where you extinguish house fires, salvage and neutralize extremely toxic and hazardous substances, and accomplish many other fascinating tasks.

name: Roadworks - The Simulation
short_description: This simulation transports you to the varied work in road construction. Re-enact typical assignments and scenarios on country roads and motorways. Get to work with the asphalt mill, steamroller, marking machine and many more special vehicles.

name: Plant Fire Department - The Simulation
short_description: Welcome to the factory fire defence! You and your colleagues will combat fire in an attempt to stop its destructive power. Solve seemingly impossible tasks, and use your equipment and special vehicles as you fight the flames.

name: Professional Construction - The Simulation
short_description: Immerse yourself in the sprawling and fascinating world of road construction! Experience life on the construction site like the pros, and use heavy equipment and massive machinery.

name: Hotel Giant
short_description: Become the ultimate hotel-mogul! You now have the chance to prove your managerial and planning skills in the hotel industry.

name: Airport Simulator 3: Day & Night
short_description: The airport is a place that never sleeps. With departures, arrivals and the continuous hustle and bustle of passengers, there is rarely an opportunity for a break.

name: VoxVR
short_description: VoxVR is a creative tool that allows you to create 3D models using cubes in virtual reality.

name: Ultimate General: Civil War
short_description: Ultimate General: Civil War is a tactical real time strategy war-game. Experience the bloodiest period of U.S. history - the American Civil War of 1861-1865.

name: THE GREY MAN
short_description: An extra dimensional experience through the campgrounds of Tinderboone National Park. The Grey Man has a job to do, but what could it be?

name: Cold Vengeance
short_description: When Canada invades the USA, Sgt. Jon Dagger must run and gun his way across the ruins of America to the Frozen North to deliver Cold Vengeance.

name: Strike.is: The Game
short_description: Load your gun and dominate the best multiplayer mobile shooter game!

name: Dropship Down
short_description: Dropship Down is a fun and intense twin-stick alien shooter for up to four players.

name: Francisca
short_description: Today my parents went to Mexico for a week, and I‚Äôm gonna have to spend seven days alone in our new house.

name: Don't Disturb
short_description: Single-player puzzle adventure with a beautiful, distinctive art style and a genuinely emotional story. As a lonely dog wandering the afterlife searching for his dead master, 'Don't Disturb' explores traditional Asian views on death and the underworld.

name: DCR: Drive.Crash.Repeat
short_description: DCR: Drive.Crash.Repeat is a retro style, ludicrous auto-forward driving game with an amazing twist, and absolutely no brakes! Drive your way through tens of handcrafted levels (to the extent that each level has its own name), across different atmospheric worlds!

name: Slayer Shock
short_description: A role-playing shooter about hunting vampires in Nebraska. Take missions to patrol the streets, rescue captive humans, and weaken the undead threat. Assemble a team, hunt the vampires, and save your hometown!

name: Sig.NULL
short_description: This is a remake and expansion of an earlier PuzzleScript game, Signal. What I thought was so brilliant about the original is that while the rules never change, the level design is such that your ability to fully comprehend and exploit those rules shifts radically over time

name: Hikikomori No Chuunibyou
short_description: Hikikomori No Chuunibyou is a pseudo 8-bit platform-adventure game with beat-em-up, puzzle, and stealth elements. With its storytelling directing the player through open-ended levels, progression through each stage requires usage of parkour-like abilities and martial-arts techniques.

name: Rogue Islands
short_description: Rogue Islands is a fast-paced, first-person shooter with magic & monsters set in a procedural fantasy wilderness. Explore forests, deserts, caves and mountains. Gain in power as you eradicate a demonic horde and inch closer to the Lords of Torment.

name: Phantasmagoria 2: A Puzzle of Flesh
short_description: All Curtis wants is to live a normal, happy life, but something seems to have other plans...

name: Phantasmagoria
short_description: Master storyteller Roberta Williams challenges you to experience the ultimate interactive nightmare.

name: Acan's Call: Act 1
short_description: Sword and Shield in hand, fight your way along this sword-fighting experience, exclusively for VR.

name: Axis Football 2016
short_description: Axis Football is a an American football simulation featuring innovative aimed passing and massive customization.

name: Space Ribbon - Slipstream to the Extreme
short_description: The ultimate slipstream racer! The aim of game is to chase down a giant space beast and race to enter the creature‚Äôs mouth as it spews out a series of different psychedelic racetracks. Slipstream to the extreme and beat your opponents to the finish line! Modify your junked up classic car and compete to become the intergalactic winner.

name: Robots In The Wild
short_description: Robots In The Wild is a challenging puzzle/strategy game about creatively dropping Blocks to build Robot fortresses. Travel to distant planets and construct huge, interconnected Robot strongholds to protect and rescue the HEARTS from the Monsters of the Wild.

name: What Remains of Edith Finch
short_description: What Remains of Edith Finch is a collection of strange tales about a family in Washington state. As Edith, you‚Äôll explore the colossal Finch house, searching for stories as she explores her family history and tries to figure out why she's the last one in her family left alive.

name: Venture Forth
short_description: Venture Forth is an extremely challenging adventure game with a retro 90s shooter vibe. Forge your own path within its labyrinthine caves but beware the danger lurking around every corner.

name: The Shrouded Isle
short_description: Includes the Sunken Sins free DLC! Your Excellency, in this short game, we prepare for the awakening of our Lord. He hungers for human sacrifice. Sinners try to hide their dark secrets, but all must be purged...

name: Dimension Hunter VR
short_description: Dimension Hunter allows you to immerse yourself in this tongue in cheek, over the top, retro-arcade experience, with a unique choice of free or railed movement. Fast paced, hardcore, fluid gameplay mechanics with a unique, and yet familiar, comic book style of carnage and gore.

name: SOS: SPECIAL OPERATIVE STORIES
short_description: These are the tense, action-packed stories of a special operative's past.

name: Blue Solar: Chaos War
short_description: Introducing Blue Solar: Chaos War, a roguelike sci-fi space adventure. Become a trader, pirate, adventurer and more. Shape a randomly generated universe. Invest in economies, engage in war, and compete for planets for your chosen government. Unite the universe, or lay waste to it all.

name: Stars
short_description: „ÄäStars„Äãis a VR game about stars. you can completely relax, look up at the sky and listen to the story of each constellation.

name: Puzzle Cross
short_description: Puzzle Cross is a Virtual Reality Nonogram Puzzles game.

name: Lost Socks: Naughty Brothers
short_description: Set off in chase of the lost Sock! Lost Socks: Naughty Brothers is a brand new platformer set in a crazy world, with infinite fun and hardcore challenges. What sets this game apart is that the main character simply can‚Äôt stop, so the onslaught of enemies, barbs and bullets will be intense!

name: Black Moon Chronicles
short_description: You are Wishmerill, a half-elf on a quest for power in a medieval world. Choose your side and lead your troops to victory!

name: SturmFront - The Mutant War: √úbel Edition
short_description: Arcade action game in the vein of Commando, Ikari Warriors and Shock Troopers, mixed with bullet hell elements. You play as an experimental cyborg battle unit fighting against unrelenting mutant hordes to a soundtrack of aggressive heavy metal and psychedelic electronica.

name: Bulletstorm: Full Clip Edition
short_description: Step into the boots of Grayson Hunt after a crash landing on an old resort planet forces him to make a hard choice: survival or revenge. Execute masterful kills with Bulletstorm: Full Clip Edition‚Äôs unique combat system that rewards you for performing the most creative and deadly kills imaginable.

name: CyberLink ActionDirector 3
short_description: ActionDirector is for the action camera enthusiast. It's the ultimate action cam accessory and the best way to create powerful action videos that showcase all the excitement of your footage. On top of that it's incredibly quick and easy to use, putting the power of movie making into the hands of even complete beginners.

name: Secret Santa
short_description: Sneak around children, pets, and the elderly as you deliver Christmas joy. Complete the list of deliveries, and have some cookies.

name: Wild Terra Online
short_description: Wild Terra Online is a sandbox RPG, in a completely player-controlled medieval world. You will have to survive in a forest full of predators, build a shelter and improve your crafts skills, tame animals and fight for treasures. You can become anyone and do whatever you want!

name: GI Racing 2.0
short_description: Experience the thrill of GI Racing 2.0! Race your way through career mode collecting trophies and earning contracts with more prestigious racing teams. Unlock and drive new cars with different capabilities, perfect for enjoying the different weather, visibility, day/night and dynamic track conditions.

name: Kuraburo Kai
short_description: Kuraburo kai has been designed to maximize the brisk and easy feeling of blasting through blocks to your heart's content. In this unique block-breaker, you can charge up your Shuriken to launch piercing throws, or use your Ninjyutu skills to blast through obstacles.

name: Moribund
short_description: Local multiplayer mayhem for 2 to 4 players in a post apocalyptic setting. Invite your friends and straight up murder them. In the game. Not in real life...

name: Arcanum: Of Steamworks and Magick Obscura
short_description: Imagine a place of wonder, where magick and technology coexist in an uneasy balance, and an adventurer might just as easily wield a flintlock pistol as a flaming sword. Welcome to the land of Arcanum.

name: Riddles Of The Past
short_description: Riddles Of The Past is a Hidden Object game with detective story and post apocalyptic atmosphere.

name: Tails
short_description: Master the evergrowing dragon in virtual reality. Tails is a roomscale VR game for the HTC Vive. Collect lanterns in order to grow the tail of your dragon. The game is easy to pick up but hard to master, and ensures a fun challenge for the whole family.

name: House of Alice
short_description: The latest release of Indie game House of Alice is now available on Steam! Explore new scenes and characters. Unlike many VR games, this virtual bunny hunt starts out in a beautiful real-looking house. You can pick up vases and candlesticks and throw them around for an exciting crash or chase after the rabbits to collect points.

name: GET THE GEMS
short_description: OLDSCHOOL game in the style of Boulder Dash / Emerald Mine. No fancy graphics, no high resolution, no holding hands. OLDSCHOOL PLAYERS ONLY !!!

name: Endangered
short_description: Aliens are invading Earth and are taking out Earths military assets. Join them in the conquest of planet Earth.

name: Super Pixel Racers
short_description: Featuring simple and satisfying drifting and nitro mechanics, Super Pixel Racers lets players race it out in numerous modes from classic Rally to pixelated mayhem in Takedown.

name: Extravaganza Rising
short_description: Fortune favors those bold enough to collect and train tiny monsters.Three brave souls boldly descend into a town ridden with monsters, allies and everything in between. Driven only by the promise of powerful trinkets, unlimited treasure and almost certain death, they venture on.

name: Emerland Solitaire: Endless Journey
short_description: Welcome to Emerland Solitaire, the land of card magic! An incredible journey awaits you, in a beautiful world filled with dwarfs, elves, mermaids and many other amazing creatures.

name: C.S.S. CITADEL VR
short_description: Are you ready to survive and escape from the C.S.S. CITADEL?

name: Fishing: Barents Sea
short_description: Commercial fishing on the Barents Sea! Take the helm of your very own fishing boat in Fishing: Barents Sea and explore the vastness of the Barents Sea in search for the best fishing zones. Start out small and earn officially licensed Scanmar Equipment and the officially licensed Hermes trawler.

name: Design it, Drive it : Speedboats
short_description: Design and drive your own speedboats with simulation quality physics including blowover/chine walk/porpoising dynamics. Popular with real life boat racers. Free drive anywhere or compete on courses through leaderboards. 40+ adjustable design parameters. Solo developer.

name: Mount Wingsuit
short_description: Welcome to Mount Wingsuit, where the thrill of hurtling down a mountain side in immersive VR with fast-paced arcade style gameplay will keep you in the zone for hours at a time.

name: Ben and Ed - Blood Party
short_description: Welcome to the Blood Party! Play together with up to 3 people and compete in deadly game shows. Customize your zombie, build your own levels, share them via Steam Workshop and die a lot.

name: A Tale of Caos: Overture
short_description: An epic journey begins! Terry, a brilliant, messy girl, is beginning her greatest adventure, following her master, Albion McMaster, whose goals are quite dark and mysterious. With Heimlich, her mechanical owl and best friend, Terry will travel through amazing worlds and many unpredictable dangers!

name: QUACK ATTACK 1985: TURBO DX EDITION
short_description: Duckster doesn't give a crap about any one or any thing.

name: Final Fleet
short_description: A lone interstellar fleet must travel across a distant and perilous galaxy in the hope of reaching safety. Final Fleet is a Virtual Reality fleet building, space shooter.

name: VRMultigames
short_description: Play several original minigames designed for VR. This free collection of minigames is designed specifically for VR from the start, and provides original games and experiments for people to try.

name: SoulHunt
short_description: SoulHunt is a ‚ÄòHide ‚Äòn Seek‚Äô multiplayer game.

name: Emergence ·µ†
short_description: Fractal Explorer and editor for VR

name: Fist of Physics
short_description: Punch a robot in the face! Robots are running wild in San Francisco. Fight through multiple rounds against different opponents to save the city. Fist of Physics uses Midas‚Äô VR physics to let players literally reach out and touch their opponent. Every response and movement looks real.

name: Simple VR Video Player
short_description: Watch your videos in virtual reality with Simple VR Video Player, an easy to use video player with full motion control support and an intuitive interface. Simple VR Video Player can play your saved video files with 2D/180¬∞/360¬∞ and 3D/SBS/OU support.

name: Kitty Cat: Jigsaw Puzzles
short_description: Kitty Cat: Jigsaw Puzzles is the puurfect game to cat lovers and jigsaw puzzle game enthusiasts. The game includes 84 challenging jigsaw puzzles with beautiful pictures of sweet, irresistible and adorable cats and kittens.

name: Puppy Dog: Jigsaw Puzzles
short_description: Puppy Dog: Jigsaw Puzzles is the perfect game to dog lovers and jigsaw puzzle game enthusiasts. The game includes 84 challenging jigsaw puzzles with beautiful pictures of irresistible cute puppies.

name: Tormentor‚ùåPunisher
short_description: Everything in Tormentor‚ùåPunisher can be killed in one hit, from bosses to yourself. Bosses conjure traps to make the arena hellish. Demons adjust to your play style and punish you. Perform combos on enemies and gain cool upgrades. Reload your machine gun by firing your shotgun. Let's do this!

name: Jockey Rush
short_description: Take the role of a jockey and ride racecourses around the world aiming to build your reputation and become the No.1. jockey!

name: Glider Island
short_description: Experience the adrenaline of hang gliding in VR! Compete for the high score to win Monthly Prizes. Collect all hoops placed around each island before time is up. Use your rocket boosters to keep from falling from the sky and avoid the dangers tossed your way!

But Pharaoh, furious with the decision of leaving by his best warrior, kidnaps his beloved Salama and orders to be imprisoned behind the Asorom door. name: Urlaubsflug Simulator ‚Äì Holiday Flight Simulator
short_description: Without doubt flying virtual aircraft from your PC is one of the most interesting simulations ‚Äì at the same time, it is one with a very steep learning curve. Holiday Flight Simulator, though, makes it especially easy to relive the last holiday trip from the cockpit‚Äôs view.

name: Epic Flail
short_description: Epic Flail is a fast paced 2D brawler with a gladiator theme that mimics the action packed fighting scenes from Japanese anime. Epic Flail has the player trapped in the arena, fighting through different modes and defeating other arena legends and even the gods themselves.

name: Firefight
short_description: Firefight is a World War II real-time simulation game similar in style to the old Close Combat series but brought up to date with better AI, individual soldier modelling, a faster frame rate to give more intense and realistic combat and an easy to use command interface.

name: Weather Lord: Legendary Hero Collector's Edition
short_description: Call upon the gods of Olympus to help you rescue your beloved before all hope is gone! Unfolding with the scope of an epic fantasy adventure, Weather Lord: Legendary Hero ‚Äì Collector's Edition will capture your imagination even as it draws you into hours of compelling gameplay!

name: Copter and Sky
short_description: You will control a modern RC hexacopter in different gamemodes!

name: Ultimate Booster Experience
short_description: Take a ride on a huge 200m (600ft) swing with breathtaking views or try other height challenges! A vast modern city is your playground. Height and speed are your passion. Ultimate height experience for VR!

name: Medieval Kingdom Wars
short_description: Rewrite medieval history through bloody siege combat in a fusion of RTS and Grand Strategy genres. Rule, build, and serve your King as a minor lord in medieval Europe. Experience siege, field and naval combat with an unseen degree of brutality. Rogue-like progression, epic towns and battles await‚Ä¶

name: Redswood VR
short_description: Redswood VR is a virtual retelling of the Red Riding Hood story. In this tale, you play as both Red and then the Huntsman, each separately tasked with making their way through a dying and unrecognizable forest from their pasts to the inevitable conclusion at Granny's house.

name: Aaero
short_description: Speed through stunning, stylised environments tracing ribbons of light, releasing the energy in the music. Battle strange enemies and fight epic boss battles all driven by an incredible licensed soundtrack.

name: Pulse Shift
short_description: Crazy physics toy with various of abilities such as gravity and time manipulation in many abstract levels.

name: Ascension VR
short_description: Now updated with the War of Shadows expansion and support for motion controls! Come try out the expansion with the devs, Tuesday nights at 8pm Pacific. Ascension VR is the first deckbuilding Virtual Reality experience.

name: WyVRn: Dragon Flight VR

name: SurvHive

name: Lord Mayor
short_description: A strategy game that lets you build cities, solve puzzles and create an empire!

name: Turner

name: Tower of Archeos

name: The Path of Greatest Resistance

name: Star Fields
short_description: Star Fields is a casual, arcade style game with strategy and shooter elements. Simple, fast paced game-play, enjoy the original electronic/progressive/synth/retrowave soundtrack or import your own mp3s and listen to them while you play!

name: klocki

name: Tomato Jones

name: Dragons Never Cry

name: The Turing Test

name: Wake Up

name: Inklings
short_description: Inklings is a beautiful Lemmings-style puzzler featuring artsy hand drawn and painted levels. Use your ingenuity to guide the otherwise hapless Inklings into the goal with an array of fantastical items including the portal gun, flip gravity, and more.

name: Way of Redemption
short_description: Way of Redemption is the perfect combination of sports and action games. Up to 4 players will be challenged with endless and frenzied games, frenetic action and competitiveness, where you must win redemption from the gods and destroy the enemy portal by throwing the ball.

name: Mustache in Hell

name: WarBirds Dawn of Aces, World War I Air Combat

name: DUO

name: Balloon Chair Death Match

name: Pro Strategy Football 2016

name: Dark Parables: Rise of the Snow Queen Collector's Edition

name: Dark Parables: The Red Riding Hood Sisters Collector's Edition

name: Puzzle Nebula

name: Extreme Forklifting 2
short_description: Always dreamed of becoming a forklift operator? Now you can!

name: ASRECorp

name: The Shadowland

Help him find the way back through treacherous obstacles and threatening foes.Prepare to rely heavily on your reflexes to complete 30+ levels spanning through 6 locations, and beat 3 unique bosses. short_description: Red Planet: Survive is a first person survival game for Microsoft Windows. Surviving in the harsh conditions of the Red Planet will be hard, but if you are strong enough, you will succeed. Find the best way to survive, but be careful, since each wrong step will ensure your demise. The environment is your main enemy.

name: Mind Spheres
short_description: Inspired by two not so different worlds, Mind Spheres brings you an exclusive and awesome experience. A physics puzzle with minigolf + pinball unique mashup. Figure out puzzles in order to proceed to the next level.

name: In The Shadow Of The Truth
short_description: First person shooter,puzzle,psychological horror video game. by 7TPGAMES

name: Doodle WHAT?!

name: Destiny of Ancient Kingdoms‚Ñ¢

name: Plates

name: Second Death

name: Underground Keeper

name: Shape Shifter

name: Rise
short_description: Rise is a first-person platformer combining casual gameplay mechanics with demanding challenges.

name: Construct: Escape the System
short_description: ‚ÄûFirst person platforming gameplay at its very best!‚Äú Construct: Escape the System is a sci-fi themed first person platformer that sees you trapped in a computer system, trying to escape. Explore the system and discover the 8 empowering 'ability orbs'.

name: FootRock

name: DJ Streamer

name: Pichon

name: MIGHT
short_description: MIGHT is a team arena brawler with fun and fast-paced combat. Choose from many different classes, each with their own unique style. Classes are easy to pick up and play but mastering them is harder.

name: Wrong Dimension - The One Dimensional Platformer
short_description: Platform and fight across a variety of levels through one dimension. What happens when you're given the familiar concepts of a 2D platformer, but seen from a different angle? Things change entirely.

name: Always Higher
short_description: Always Higher is a single-player sci-fi adventure shooter VR game. Play as a secret agent, collect data modules, avoid enemy soldiers and escape underground facility!

name: PD Particles 9
short_description: "This is the ‚ÄòLight‚Äô or entry-level version of the amazingly powerful PD Howler - the digital painting program for Windows, powered by Project Dogwaffle.

name: Gabriel Knight¬Æ 3: Blood of the Sacred, Blood of the Damned
short_description: Play as both Gabriel Knight and Grace Nakimura as you learn more about what is hidden in the hills of France.

name: The Challenge
short_description: The early 22nd century began the era of "time travel". At this time, the UN Security Council also created the "Time Bureau", a special surveillance service where employees are required to eliminate anachronisms caused by people visiting past events.

name: Life is Feudal: Forest Village

Shape, build and expand your settlement, grow various food to prevent your villagers from avitaminosis and starvation. Possess them for additional micromanagement or simply to wander around.

It is a casual yet challenging game, reminiscent of the early days of video games, but with a more modern feel. Vex is a crowdfunded indie game, built with love and character in mind.

name: Pigmentone

name: Noob Squad

name: Crystal Cosmos
short_description: Crystal Cosmos is a side scrolling color-based space shooter. You need to match your ship's color to your enemies color in order to destroy them.

name: Push The Crate: Remastered Edition
short_description: Push The Crate: Remastered Edition is a 3D transport puzzle game with 100 level. Now remastered with improved visuals, UI and gameplay mechanics.

name: Monster Slayers

name: Empty Horizons

name: Maze Roller

name: SweatShop
short_description: SweatShop is a incremental game where you're the owner of a sweatshop, you have to hire more staff to work for you and sell products to gain more money. Buy many different upgrades for your workers and make even more money than before.

name: Adventures On The Polluted Islands
short_description: Adventures On The Polluted Islands ‚Äì adventure game with elements of sandbox. You will play a small crab, armed with a boomerang. Help the survivors and go in search of salvation. Tasks, secrets, boss fights, easter eggs and much more are waiting for you!

name: Sorcerer King: Rivals
short_description: Explore a rich fantasy world, go on quests for powerful weapons, and forge a new civilization in Sorcerer King: Rivals. Can you build a civilization to topple the malevolent Sorcerer King and become a god yourself?

name: Discovering Space 2
short_description: Discovering Space 2 is all about exploration. There‚Äôs no action, shooting or explosions, just sightseeing, discovery and relaxation on an epic scale.Calming, wondrous and adventurous.

name: The Housewife

She believes that he only beats her when she disappoints him. Get deep inside the functioning psyche of a victim of abuse.

name: The Beast Within: A Gabriel Knight¬Æ Mystery

name: Nothin' But Net

name: MegaTagmension Blanc + Neptune VS Zombies (Neptunia)

short_description: Ruction is an open world adventure game where you embark on a journey through a jungle environment looking for clues that lead to your lost brother, and along the way discover the mystery of the golden tablet.

name: Brick Battalion

name: Dark Parables: The Swan Princess and The Dire Tree Collector's Edition
short_description: Treachery to behold!

name: Geo-Fall
short_description: Geo-Fall is an action packed room-scale game in which you collect and sort orbs to get the highest score possible!

name: Space, VR!
short_description: Space, VR! is VR in Space!

name: LaserCat

name: Senza Peso
short_description: As a soul transitioning into the afterlife, Senza Peso shepherds you on a spiritual journey through a beautifully dark world of lost souls and redemption.

name: Watching Grass Grow In VR - The Game

name: Paddle Up

Caught up in the turmoil, can she make it back home?

name: Deep Dark Dungeon
short_description: Deep Dark Dungeon is a rogue-lite action game in which the player dives into the deep, dark depths of various dungeons filled with bad-tempered monsters that will attack them on sight.

name: Kingdom: New Lands
short_description: Kingdom: New Lands builds upon the award-winning gameplay and mystery of Kingdom by introducing an abundance of new content to the IGF-nominated title while maintaining the simplicity and depth that legions of monarchs have come to experience and enjoy.

name: Momento Temporis: Light from the Deep
short_description: All alone, Hania sets out on a journey to find the answers to her past across this uncharted, perilous and magical world.

name: Running Gods
short_description: Become the Divinest God!

name: Fighting Fantasy Legends
short_description: Create your own adventures in a dangerous land of monsters, treasures and traps. From renowned authors Steve Jackson and Ian Livingstone (co-founders of Games Workshop) and Nomad Games, Fighting Fantasy Legends is a role-playing card game set in the world of Fighting Fantasy.

name: Supipara - Chapter 1 Spring Has Come!
short_description: Spring has come, and our protagonist, Yukinari, returns home after 7 years. Between his second cousin Sakura, who meets him outside in a full maid outfit, Hotaru, a half-Japanese beauty with a sharp tongue, and the lazy scheming witch Alice - life just got way more interesting!

short_description: Car racing but different. Enjoy the realistic RC car physics engine of these mini cars on different routes, in various lighting conditions, indoor and outdoor! Prove your driving skills early, so that you have soon enough money to buy new faster RC models and other routes.

name: Shiny

name: Dashy Square VR

Your mission is to get into a long time abandoned base, suddenly taken over by some kind of private military, find your way up and destroy the source of a signal comming from the base. name: Deios II // DEIDIA

name: Free Balling
short_description: Why not testy it out?

You should swap Chips with each other to combine their pins into solid Chain from Source to Receiver.

name: Montaro
short_description: Montaro is a DOGE.

Tang Haiyin and Yao Fengxi came to his life as well. An unexpected accident had involved them together.

name: TrumPi√±ata

name: Ancient VR coaster

If it touches the wire, or you don't complete it in time, then the buzzer will sound and you will fail.

name: STANDBY

name: EARTH'S DAWN

name: VR: Vacate the Room (Virtual Reality Escape)

name: ViveSpray

name: VeeR Pong

name: Ranger of the jungle

name: Haven Moon

name: Awakened

You see, it's a series of minigames within the game and they're all tied together by a growing and riveting storyline that'll entertain you, challenge you, scare you, and keep...

name: #Archery

name: Jonah's Path

name: Rivais Em Batalha

name: Dungeons 3

name: NeverMine

short_description: Snow, dullness, depression. Constant dissatisfaction with work and superiors and feeling like there is no escape. Is this what life will always be? Perhaps‚Ä¶ but I can always hope for change to be just around the corner!‚Ä¶

name: Disgraced

name: Mad Combat Marines

name: NAL Is Alive

name: Dungeon Journey

name: Smithy

name: Milford Heaven - Luken's Chronicles
short_description: Milford Heaven, a small medieval village, is under attack!! Won't you do nothing? Luken's castle is filled with treasures! Come, help the villagers, loot Luken's castle and became as rich as you have never dreamed before!

name: Citadel
short_description: Citadel is an indie cooperative survival game with rogue-like elements inspired by ‚ÄúCube‚Äù the movie.

name: OESE
short_description: OESE - The space survival game about decisions and consequences.

name: Pick a Hero
short_description: Card drafting strategy

name: Brazed
short_description: Brazed is a game about escaping the unknown planet.

name: Genius Greedy Mouse
short_description: GENIUS GREEDY MOUSE is a clay based puzzle game featuring a host of fun and challenging levels.

name: Campaign Clicker

name: Karma Miwa

name: Shift

name: Magnetta

The players compete to be the last robot standing; using a charged burst of speed called the JOLT, and an array of different objects in the environment.

name: Impossible Quest

name: Beekyr Reloaded

name: Evil Maze
short_description: Random Iiem and Skills + Hidden elements RPG + Strategy ARPG The game starts in a dark underground maze where a female officer is confined in a prison. She wants to get out of this nightmare maze! Would you like to help her?

name: Alveari
short_description: A collection of VR mini-games! Slow motion action!

name: Cthulhu Realms
short_description: Star Realms has gone insane! Introducing Cthulhu Realms! Are you zany enough to play the crazier and creepier cousin of Star Realms? Download and play today to find out why Cthulhu Realms is so crazily addictive!

name: PLANET ALPHA

name: Nurse Love Addiction

name: PolyDome
